summary: Its time to give the dragon born his/her own castle player home, Very beta
descriptionHtml:
To start, its north west of whiterun. You could get lost in this place. It has its own forge systems, vampire court, hunting hall, Cozy private room, Prison and cells, Your own guards and some trainer followers. It has a bar/dance floor archery range, hall of magic, adoption childrens bedroom. It will have a kitchen, dining hall,chapel
Its an on going project so keep in mind its not at all done.
author: Waylon Peckham
